{"tid":1830232,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)特務型戰 史密夫決戰史密妻 凸務Madam","createTime":"2020-01-19T12:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T17:54:31.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf56c5cb0cdb386f98d6c8ddcbf86f4cbd67b90","tid":1830232,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T12:21:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沙士又殺入黎香港 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=89f7e33d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=1fc8aea4\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=72f3b539\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/01/The_Man_from_U.N.C.L.E._Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F01%2FThe_Man_from_U.N.C.L.E._Poster.jpg&h=221fe847&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f2/Movie_poster_Mr.&amp;Mrs._Smith.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff2%2FMovie_poster_Mr.%26Mrs._Smith.jpg&h=b1f8ab42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/5d/Spy2015_TeaserPoster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F5d%2FSpy2015_TeaserPoster.jpg&h=8e121664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事背景定於1960年代的冷戰時期，美國中央情報局（CIA）特務拿破崙&middot;蘇洛（亨利&middot;卡維爾飾）和蘇聯國安局（KGB）特務伊利亞&middot;科里亞金（艾米&middot;漢默飾）被迫合作，阻止一個神秘的國際犯罪組織 「T.H.R.U.S.H.[註 1]」，原來這個組織是納粹餘黨，他們綁架了一名核武專家泰勒博士（克里斯丁&middot;伯克飾），意圖引爆第三次世界大戰，蘇洛與科里亞金找到了專家住在東柏林的愛女蓋比&middot;泰勒（艾莉西亞&middot;薇坎德飾）..<br />\n<br />\n2.約翰&middot;史密斯在出任務到哥倫比亞的波哥大時，巧遇到一位名叫珍的女人，兩人在六星期後閃電結婚。<br />\n結婚六年後，似乎原本的激情被磨平，生活漸漸變得平淡無趣。史密斯夫妻兩人都是職業殺手，雖然已經成為夫妻六年，但卻不知道對方的真實身份。直到有一天，雙方被各自的殺手公司指派暗殺同一人的任務，才讓兩人發現彼此的秘密。一開始兩人想要幹掉對方，後來又不忍下手<br />\n<br />\n3.一名美國中央情報局（CIA）內勤數據分析師蘇珊&middot;庫柏（梅莉莎&middot;麥卡錫飾），長期協助著外勤探員布萊德利&middot;范恩（裘德&middot;洛飾）。胖胖的蘇珊，是個傑出的數據分析專家，也是范恩的左右手，長期合作之下，對俊俏的范恩有著若有似無的情愫。但范恩與美女軍火商蕾娜&middot;波楊諾（蘿絲&middot;拜恩飾）交鋒時卻出師不利，讓CIA喪失了一員猛將，惡毒的蕾娜&middot;波楊諾居然還列出CIA的精銳特工名單，向中情局挑釁<br />\n<br />\n8 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=6c26ae31\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=da1fd48c\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3237d5150adb1a9614d62a615bff5212309fdb35","tid":1830232,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8048baa8584e4fc9db05fc36344f0ba7034735","tid":1830232,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48fcf64b0f62c08cf0c4bc5a580e29333623197","tid":1830232,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T14:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b6208dc5df4c12ad4a3535feb8b4c3aecc6791","tid":1830232,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb069ef775e90a7f7ed3760af6f741ef707fd6f","tid":1830232,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}